{"tid":2037624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動轉型探討","createTime":"2020-05-27T05:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T07:18:41.000Z","uid":34006,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4cb9e723414cea3771f386e76d284a9dae84ca","tid":2037624,"uid":34006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"今朝當黑警要提防黎明行動式堵路果陣, 佢地分散左警力喺d交通要點到 (e.g. 幾隻軍裝狗喺公路既行人天橋)<br />\n<br />\n但各個交通要點有既狗數量<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔多</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵在明, 我在暗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n會唔會各區既手足都可以針對到守自己果區交通要點既狗做到d野?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">e.g. 街妨圍屌, 勇武自由發揮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前提係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">果個要點既狗得幾隻</span></span>, 紅隧果d成堆防暴都好難"},{"pid":"1504167a116d316c90e06fbe2db74e497099d861","tid":2037624,"uid":306337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"點解要黎明 唔可以暗夜?<br />\n當初魚蛋都係2點打撚到天光。<br />\n我唔明點解要凌晨5點<br />\n明明2 3點仲易"},{"pid":"44a29ee8f169f629f0fc724dd4b776caaabe191a","tid":2037624,"uid":29381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:57:43.000Z","msg":"黎明行動一早已經狗多過人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0affe14ac0396af32c36a87d97efe196971d40b","tid":2037624,"uid":34006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a29ee8f169f629f0fc724dd4b776caaabe191a","tid":2037624,"uid":29381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:57:43.000Z","msg":"黎明行動一早已經狗多過人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"i mean自己區既交通要點<br />\n<br />\n你望下自己區公路條行人天橋係得幾隻, 定成隊？"},{"pid":"c6d4ea43ced398d5bf9639eaf0fffc8b5a843d79","tid":2037624,"uid":34006